<div class="dablink">"Ganapati" redirects here. For <a href="/wiki/Hindu" title="Hindu" class="mw-redirect">Hindu</a> <a href="/wiki/Historical_Vedic_religion" title="Historical Vedic religion">Vedic</a> Deity and God of planet <a href="/wiki/Jupiter" title="Jupiter">Jupiter</a>, see <a href="/wiki/Brihaspati" title="Brihaspati" class="mw-redirect">Brihaspati</a>.</div>
<div class="dablink">For stories mentioning Ganesha's attributes, see <a href="/wiki/Mythological_anecdotes_of_Ganesha" title="Mythological anecdotes of Ganesha">Mythological anecdotes of Ganesha</a>.</div>
