<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREF.C5.9A.C4.81stri_Khiste1991">Śāstri Khiste, <span lang="sa-Latn" title="International Alphabet of Sanskrit Transliteration" class="Unicode" style="white-space:normal; text-decoration: none" xml:lang="sa-Latn">Baṭukanātha</span> (1991), <i><span lang="sa-Latn" title="International Alphabet of Sanskrit Transliteration" class="Unicode" style="white-space:normal; text-decoration: none" xml:lang="sa-Latn">Gaṇeśasahasranāmastotram: mūla evaṁ srībhāskararāyakṛta ‘khadyota’ vārtika sahita</span></i>, <span lang="sa-Latn" title="International Alphabet of Sanskrit Transliteration" class="Unicode" style="white-space:normal; text-decoration: none" xml:lang="sa-Latn">Vārāṇasī</span>: Prācya Prakāśana</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=%3Cspan+lang%3D%22sa-Latn%22+xml%3Alang%3D%22sa-Latn%22+title%3D%22International+Alphabet+of+Sanskrit+Transliteration%22++class%3D%22Unicode%22+style%3D%22white-space%3Anormal%3B+text-decoration%3A+none%22%3EGa%E1%B9%87e%C5%9Basahasran%C4%81mastotram%3A+m%C5%ABla+eva%E1%B9%81+sr%C4%ABbh%C4%81skarar%C4%81yak%E1%B9%9Bta+%E2%80%98khadyota%E2%80%99+v%C4%81rtika+sahita%3C%2Fspan%3E&amp;rft.aulast=%C5%9A%C4%81stri+Khiste&amp;rft.aufirst=%3Cspan+lang%3D%22sa-Latn%22+xml%3Alang%3D%22sa-Latn%22+title%3D%22International+Alphabet+of+Sanskrit+Transliteration%22++class%3D%22Unicode%22+style%3D%22white-space%3Anormal%3B+text-decoration%3A+none%22%3EBa%E1%B9%ADukan%C4%81tha%3C%2Fspan%3E&amp;rft.au=%C5%9A%C4%81stri+Khiste%2C+%3Cspan+lang%3D%22sa-Latn%22+xml%3Alang%3D%22sa-Latn%22+title%3D%22International+Alphabet+of+Sanskrit+Transliteration%22++class%3D%22Unicode%22+style%3D%22white-space%3Anormal%3B+text-decoration%3A+none%22%3EBa%E1%B9%ADukan%C4%81tha%3C%2Fspan%3E&amp;rft.date=1991&amp;rft.place=%3Cspan+lang%3D%22sa-Latn%22+xml%3Alang%3D%22sa-Latn%22+title%3D%22International+Alphabet+of+Sanskrit+Translite