<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREF.C5.9A.C4.81stri1978">Śāstri, Hargovinda (1978), <i><span lang="sa-Latn" title="International Alphabet of Sanskrit Transliteration" class="Unicode" style="white-space:normal; text-decoration: none" xml:lang="sa-Latn">Amarkoṣa</span> with Hindi commentary</i>, Vārānasi: Chowkhambā Sanskrit Series Office</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=%3Cspan+lang%3D%22sa-Latn%22+xml%3Alang%3D%22sa-Latn%22+title%3D%22International+Alphabet+of+Sanskrit+Transliteration%22++class%3D%22Unicode%22+style%3D%22white-space%3Anormal%3B+text-decoration%3A+none%22%3EAmarko%E1%B9%A3a%3C%2Fspan%3E+with+Hindi+commentary&amp;rft.aulast=%C5%9A%C4%81stri&amp;rft.aufirst=Hargovinda&amp;rft.au=%C5%9A%C4%81stri%2C+Hargovinda&amp;rft.date=1978&amp;rft.place=V%C4%81r%C4%81nasi&amp;rft.pub=Chowkhamb%C4%81+Sanskrit+Series+Office&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Ganesha"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
